-- Etihad Says Carried Record Number of Passengers, Cargo in 2011
-- B y   T a m a r a   W a l i d
-- 2012-01-15T12:17:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-15/etihad-says-carried-record-number-of-passengers-cargo-in-2011.html
Etihad Airways  carried a record
number of passengers and cargo in 2011 as  Abu Dhabi ’s state-
owned carrier added flights and destinations.  The airline, which last month announced increasing its
stake in  Air Berlin Plc (AB1)  to 29.2 percent, carried 8.29 million
travelers last year, up 17 percent from 2010, the company said
in an e-mailed statement today. Etihad’s Crystal Cargo unit
transported 310,000 tons, an increase of 18 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tamara Walid in Dubai at   twalid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas in Berlin at 
